Note that these approaches, unlike KMS/DRM, will not typically allow to output to multiple screens from the same application. trans-unit.source: Over time, an application will allocate large portions of memory, write data to that memory, and subsequently free some portions of it once it has finished using some of the data. This can result in "free" memory being located in non-contiguous chunks, which cannot be returned to the operating system for other applications to use. It also has an impact on the caching and access characteristics of the application, as the "living" data may be spread across many different pages of physical memory. This in turn could force the operating system to swap, which can cause filesystem I/O - which is, comparatively speaking, an extremely slow operation.

trans-unit.source: Path items are rendered by performing OpenGL calls using the GL_NV_path_rendering extension. This is the default on NVIDIA hardware when the default, OpenGL Qt Quick scenegraph backend is in use.
trans-unit.target: 通过使用 GL_NV_path_rendering 扩展执行OpenGL调用来渲染路径项。当使用默认的OpenGL Qt Quick Scenegraph后端时，这是NVIDIA硬件上的默认值。

trans-unit.source: PathAngleArc provides a simple way of specifying an arc. While PathArc is designed to work as part of a larger path (specifying start and end), PathAngleArc is designed to make a path where the arc is primary (such as a circular progress indicator) more intuitive.
trans-unit.target: PathAngleArc提供了一种指定圆弧的简单方法。虽然PathArc被设计为作为较大路径的一部分（指定起点和终点），但PathAngleArc却被设计为使弧为主要路径（例如圆形进度指示器）的路径更加直观。

trans-unit.source: PathArc provides a simple way of specifying an arc that ends at a given position and uses the specified radius. It is modeled after the SVG elliptical arc command.
trans-unit.target: PathArc提供了一种简单的方法来指定一个以给定位置为终点并使用指定半径的圆弧。它是以SVG椭圆弧命令为模型的。

trans-unit.source: PathInterpolator provides x, y, and angle information for a particular progress along a path.
trans-unit.target: PathInterpolator为沿路径的特定 progress 提供 x ， y 和 angle 信息。

trans-unit.source: PathPercent allows you to manipulate the spacing between items on a PathView's path. You can use it to bunch together items on part of the path, and spread them out on other parts of the path.
trans-unit.target: PathPercent允许您操纵PathView路径上项目之间的间距。您可以使用它在路径的一部分上将项目组合在一起，然后将它们散布在路径的其他部分上。

trans-unit.source: PathView attaches a number of properties to the root item of the delegate, for example PathView.isCurrentItem.
